data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home in Emperor Estates! Displaying a 2-car garage, RV gate, & a desert landscape. Discover an open layout with wall cut-outs to create a more relaxed yet private feel! Elegant light fixtures, designer paint, and carpet & wood-look tile enhance the fabulous vibe. The gourmet kitchen boasts SS appliances, glass backsplash, a pantry, Brazilian marble counters, staggered cabinetry, a bay window, and an island w/breakfast bar. Main bedroom has outdoor access and an ensuite with dual sinks, separate tub/shower, & a walk-in closet. Enjoy the backyard oasis, offering a lush lawn, shade trees, storage shed, covered & open patios, travertine, and a sparkling pool w/waterfall! Community offers biking/walking trails & playgrounds. Near the Queen Creek Marketplace! Just WOW
